Some visitors came this time also from fother Hackspaces around Lake Constance. Thus it became an international open day. Many interesting conversations and presentations about different topics took place during the whole day.


Many thanks to the waffle bakers, goulash cookers, cake dispensers, photographers, filmmakers, lecturers, organizers, builders, cleaners, helpers, explainers, hackers, visitors - all of them.
