On Saturday, 17 November 2018 the Toolbox Bodensee opened and all projects got presented to the public. Also this year there was a densely packed lecture program of different topics. The quadrocopter flight show and soldering for children have almost become a tradition. The game developer group presenting their retro games was one of the new things this year. Our new lounge with cool wall painting was used for the short lectures. Many colourful lights were in operation again.
